{"tid":1537992,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"捉哂班風向撚/化分撚/港共網軍嘅方法，推到連仔同IT狗同睇到!","createTime":"2019-09-04T06:04:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T12:43:25.000Z","uid":50904,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"e2ee96ec1233ebf3cba93672b632137a81b7df49","tid":1537992,"uid":50904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:04:26.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">點解要睇呢篇文:</span></strong></span></div><br />\n1.想唔想知台灣連登仔點分辨一個User係咪風向撚/化分撚/港共網軍?<br />\n2.想唔想知連登係咪真係咁多「僵屍AC」同「P牌打手」?<br />\n想知就拉落去睇，唔得閒就先留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n太多人只睇頭Post，我放個目錄，幫大家養成睇post習慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>回覆#2 台灣連登「PTT」分析網軍方法</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>回覆#3 從正反方向論證「僵屍帳號」、「P牌打手」係咪存在</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n利申:唔係IT狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，希望有人可以討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6994a641565c6085cff27838d3b4adf1b656c7af","tid":1537992,"uid":50904,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:04:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">背景資訊: </span></strong></div></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2Findex.html&d=8FXSm2SwW1drj%2BZzPONh3Kcrr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=6b508a9c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/index.html</a><br />\nPTT係台灣最大最耐歷史嘅嘅討論區，打個比喻就係台版連登/高登<br />\n<br />\n所以網民嘅取向都會被解讀成後生一輩嘅睇法，因此PTT成為打選戰同中共統戰台灣嘅必爭之地。<br />\n<br />\n點解韓國瑜呢啲淨係識識發大財嘅會當選，亦都被認為係同結合PTT、social media同電視/報紙嘅資訊戰有關<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">簡介PTT :</span></span></strong></div><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">TLDR: PTT會公開所有user嘅IP資料、包括最後一次Log in、開post，同回post果陣嘅 IP</span></strong><br />\n當然啦，我反對係連登公開IP address，但連仔手上一定有呢啲資料可以用黎查證<br />\n<br />\n以下可以選讀，無時間可skip<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">PTT分咗好多唔子版，\n每個版都由經子版內自行選舉嘅Admin管理\n\n當中「八掛Gossiping」流量最高，基本上就好似吹水台咁任你9up\n而「政黑HatePolitics」就係用黎批判政客，政治野會集中係度傾\n\n因為PTT真係好耐歷史，佢運作係似email多過討論區\n你想回覆一篇文有兩個做法:\n1.係原post下面推文，你reply時可以比推、-&gt;、噓3種評分\n2.Reply 原post、好似email咁出現個Re:XXX嘅新post，\n通常係正經長文回覆先用，同一標題嘅佢地叫做「討論串」\n\nPTT最特別嘅地方係佢會紀錄你嘅IP address，\n你用一個人嘅User name係可以查到佢最後一次上線嘅IP\n\n而開post嘅樓主IP係會係文章最尾度公開顯示出黎、\n2019年6月起，「八掛Gossiping」版甚至會公開埋推文者嘅IP，\n同埋標示IP來源國家</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">正文:台灣連登仔點樣捉鬼</span></span></strong></div><br />\n<strong>分析用工具網址: </strong><a href=\"https://www.ianalyseur.org/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ianalyseur.org%2F&d=8FXSm2SwW1drj%2BZzPONh3Kcrr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=ef1b9564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ianalyseur.org/</a><br />\n<br />\n我隨手拎一篇PTT「八掛Gossiping」版講香港嘅文嘅AC去做例子<br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">UserID: bearq258</div></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">1.關聯圖</span></strong>:運用IP address紀錄，分析該帳號 Login時嘅IP，並反向列出相同IP但唔同帳號嘅情況<br />\n呢條友有幾十個唔同IP、仲有廿幾個同IP唔同AC嘅情況、多到我cap唔哂<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r0g3WAg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr0g3WAg.jpg&h=fc8ba552&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">2.作息圖: </span></strong>用開post/回文時間、整理出該帳號主人嘅作息時間表<br />\n圖入面顏色越深藍=果個時間越活躍回覆，呢個人星期一至日，24小都online回post咁濟<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dvdFene.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdvdFene.jpg&h=f413a8b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">3.文字雲</span></strong><br />\n原作者解釋呢個功能嘅PTT post比人del左，所以我都唔知實際base on咩去做<br />\n我估個人估計:應該係基於標題同推文回覆中最常出現嘅字眼去調整啲詞語大細<br />\n<br />\n你可以用黎睇下呢個人最關心咩話題，但唔知佢嘅立場<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JEMb5vX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJEMb5vX.jpg&h=4b4639bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n下面係一個台灣網站對呢個工具嘅詳細介紹、有興趣可入去睇:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.astralweb.com.tw/ianalyseur/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.astralweb.com.tw%2Fianalyseur%2F&d=8FXSm2SwW1drj%2BZzPONh3Kcrr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=c85a5c78\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.astralweb.com.tw/ianalyseur/</a>"},{"pid":"a65d0de37451ce26d5c6be2d0b6b9fa9ea776a22","tid":1537992,"uid":50904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:04:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">從正反方向論證「僵屍帳號」、「P牌打手」係咪存在</div></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\nSor，我真係無資料係手，以下係我建基於搵到嘅資料去講<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個篇文係我原先回覆其他人嘅post，但我覺得可以拎出黎比更多人討論<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>A.反駁「僵屍帳號」、「P牌網軍」論</strong></span></div></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Fact:</strong>連登起底功能只能起出該用戶有無開過Post，唔會顯示回覆人地嘅Post<br />\n<br />\n<strong>「疆屍帳號」解釋:</strong>連登註冊用戶極多，直正有開過Post嘅可能只佔小部份用戶，大部份都係只讀不回/只留正負評嘅CD Rom<br />\n「疆屍帳號」可以係一班非活躍用戶，但因為極度憤怒先出上水出post/reply<br />\n<br />\n<strong>佐證1</strong>:我呢個post有 2122正評、15負評，但只有183個回覆<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1525915/\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1525915/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>佐證2</strong>:我會員no.係 50904，16年12月註冊，但第一個post係24日之前<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>「P牌打手」解釋</strong>:因連登被多次點名為成就反送中運動，大量人湧入開新AC係正常不過，人總有立場、有關心嘅事，唔好因為P牌就當人打手<br />\n<strong>Fact:</strong>偷懶唔特別搵，但高登被點名是常識吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">B.支持「僵屍帳號」、「P牌打手」論</span></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Fact1</strong>:LIHKG出過公告，表示有人以非暴力破解形式大量登入，目前發現被盜帳戶總數少於 350 個<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1459855/\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1459855/</a><br />\n<strong>「疆屍帳號」解釋</strong>:真係有組織hack人account用黎帶風向<br />\n<br />\nFact2:連登開AC條件<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5yhVNOr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5yhVNOr.jpg&h=96d288d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/170104/\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/170104/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://sites.google.com/a/lihkg.com/help/register\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsites.google.com%2Fa%2Flihkg.com%2Fhelp%2Fregister&d=8FXSm2SwW1drj%2BZzPONh3Kcrr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=b08440b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://sites.google.com/a/lihkg.com/help/register</a><br />\n<strong>「P牌打手」解釋:</strong>有人有組織地取得/非法獲取ISP/.Edu 電郵以開啟新AC、甚至用錢直買AC都唔奇<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中立講法:</span></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n反駁同支嘅講法都係可以有理據支持，兩者可以並存無矛盾<br />\nFact check方向:<br />\n我唔係IT狗，以下係我聽過嘅方法，需要連仔以Server資訊查證<br />\n1.帳號間嘅回覆/開post關係、會否經常出現一種某AC開post、其他AC必然推post嘅情形?<br />\n2.帳號一日入邊嘅上線/活躍時間，e.g.會唔會大量帳戶活躍回覆/開post時間都係朝9晚5好似返工咁? 或者 24小都online?<br />\n3.帳號之間嘅IP address有無不正常情況? e.g.大量帳戶經同一IP發佈/IP國家經常轉換等等<br />\n4.會否有以同一IP address/email provider持續註冊新AC?"},{"pid":"17d2cb283ca58f87e9f9e8fb1bce0ec91d8173c3","tid":1537992,"uid":50904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:05:10.000Z","msg":"推銷自己Post:<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">[圖多慎入] 六四天安門 = 太子8.31 ?</span><br />\n只要將兩件事嘅圖放埋一齊，大家都自然心領神會<br />\nlink入面仲有5張，入去幫手推比國際文宣戰線一齊討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RA6rNta.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRA6rNta.jpg&h=9fe78eff&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"09b15f4ad0288d21ea088ac103175a40cd3e87e6","tid":1537992,"uid":50904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:05:46.000Z","msg":"慢速自推十連<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6323ce86299212e317e6cbf4489aeac0b1fd7b4b","tid":1537992,"uid":113876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:08:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5863f8248dd8e42cfd77e6498730d8dab7944462","tid":1537992,"uid":245033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:08:55.000Z","msg":"IT狗LM先<br />\n今晚有時間研究下"},{"pid":"4523ce7b768f70e7aabf4aeee845c4adda370b16","tid":1537992,"uid":50904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:09:24.000Z","msg":"2/10 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n極速負評嘅人係咪真係無拉落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a49d085a0ffb7af6a0c3cd4a1727f2c7f70c27a","tid":1537992,"uid":50904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"17d2cb283ca58f87e9f9e8fb1bce0ec91d8173c3","tid":1537992,"uid":50904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:05:10.000Z","msg":"推銷自己Post:<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">[圖多慎入] 六四天安門 = 太子8.31 ?</span><br />\n只要將兩件事嘅圖放埋一齊，大家都自然心領神會<br />\nlink入面仲有5張，入去幫手推比國際文宣戰線一齊討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RA6rNta.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRA6rNta.jpg&h=9fe78eff&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:11:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1535155\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1535155</a><br />\n補link<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d808c31cb67bb08284a35e8bdb216a488b9a113e","tid":1537992,"uid":50904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:13:04.000Z","msg":"3/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e50049dd5345360a33c629c75d0c01497748296f","tid":1537992,"uid":50904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:15:57.000Z","msg":"4/10 長文消化需時，慢一點再評分<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ac7944f2fce469863ddf79555179472742ca8c7","tid":1537992,"uid":23046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:16:32.000Z","msg":"有心機<br />\n呢個唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd29026466a7cdc8e5f0f1bd3551630ea43d9574","tid":1537992,"uid":45007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:17:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c61406e1b2410db104e5ad4796745f32724754b7","tid":1537992,"uid":104758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:17:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba1c63d537810216e733d0a522fb225929129158","tid":1537992,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:19:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"910b9291ddf437644f5502beb307a50fd2e68247","tid":1537992,"uid":50904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:21:32.000Z","msg":"5/10 希望有更多職業IT 狗去研究<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a7d8166e3bc253d6a45408ab951fd76b5341f05","tid":1537992,"uid":279650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:21:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25225da86bc65ca307b36365bd7a7886cb95f287","tid":1537992,"uid":48935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:23:01.000Z","msg":"p牌幫推"},{"pid":"7c67275d8a56e19710231748fb5d161c7e1307fc","tid":1537992,"uid":147434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a65d0de37451ce26d5c6be2d0b6b9fa9ea776a22","tid":1537992,"uid":50904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:04:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">從正反方向論證「僵屍帳號」、「P牌打手」係咪存在</div></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\nSor，我真係無資料係手，以下係我建基於搵到嘅資料去講<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個篇文係我原先回覆其他人嘅post，但我覺得可以拎出黎比更多人討論<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>A.反駁「僵屍帳號」、「P牌網軍」論</strong></span></div></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Fact:</strong>連登起底功能只能起出該用戶有無開過Post，唔會顯示回覆人地嘅Post<br />\n<br />\n<strong>「疆屍帳號」解釋:</strong>連登註冊用戶極多，直正有開過Post嘅可能只佔小部份用戶，大部份都係只讀不回/只留正負評嘅CD Rom<br />\n「疆屍帳號」可以係一班非活躍用戶，但因為極度憤怒先出上水出post/reply<br />\n<br />\n<strong>佐證1</strong>:我呢個post有 2122正評、15負評，但只有183個回覆<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1525915/\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1525915/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>佐證2</strong>:我會員no.係 50904，16年12月註冊，但第一個post係24日之前<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>「P牌打手」解釋</strong>:因連登被多次點名為成就反送中運動，大量人湧入開新AC係正常不過，人總有立場、有關心嘅事，唔好因為P牌就當人打手<br />\n<strong>Fact:</strong>偷懶唔特別搵，但高登被點名是常識吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">B.支持「僵屍帳號」、「P牌打手」論</span></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Fact1</strong>:LIHKG出過公告，表示有人以非暴力破解形式大量登入，目前發現被盜帳戶總數少於 350 個<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1459855/\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1459855/</a><br />\n<strong>「疆屍帳號」解釋</strong>:真係有組織hack人account用黎帶風向<br />\n<br />\nFact2:連登開AC條件<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5yhVNOr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5yhVNOr.jpg&h=96d288d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/170104/\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/170104/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://sites.google.com/a/lihkg.com/help/register\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsites.google.com%2Fa%2Flihkg.com%2Fhelp%2Fregister&d=8FXSm2SwW1drj%2BZzPONh3Kcrr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=b08440b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://sites.google.com/a/lihkg.com/help/register</a><br />\n<strong>「P牌打手」解釋:</strong>有人有組織地取得/非法獲取ISP/.Edu 電郵以開啟新AC、甚至用錢直買AC都唔奇<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中立講法:</span></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n反駁同支嘅講法都係可以有理據支持，兩者可以並存無矛盾<br />\nFact check方向:<br />\n我唔係IT狗，以下係我聽過嘅方法，需要連仔以Server資訊查證<br />\n1.帳號間嘅回覆/開post關係、會否經常出現一種某AC開post、其他AC必然推post嘅情形?<br />\n2.帳號一日入邊嘅上線/活躍時間，e.g.會唔會大量帳戶活躍回覆/開post時間都係朝9晚5好似返工咁? 或者 24小都online?<br />\n3.帳號之間嘅IP address有無不正常情況? e.g.大量帳戶經同一IP發佈/IP國家經常轉換等等<br />\n4.會否有以同一IP address/email provider持續註冊新AC?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:25:28.000Z","msg":"個文字雲係根據每一組詞語出現既頻率來定隻字既SIZE<br />\n同埋仲有D USER係純回POST唔回POST 好似我咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61b6c385421834b8106518c8738f30d46f3df6b9","tid":1537992,"uid":37144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:26:23.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ad827a8373835e874ae9959ae1ad2c0e196f9017","tid":1537992,"uid":50904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:27:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個文字雲係根據每一組詞語出現既頻率來定隻字既SIZE<br />\n同埋仲有D USER係純回POST唔回POST 好似我咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/